Notes: Wildcats become the first Chico State women's team to start the season 10-0
since 1974. Courtney Hamilton posts first career double-double (12 points, 11
rebounds) while also dishing out seven assists. Wildcats on the road next
weekend vs. UC San Diego and Cal State San Bernardino.
Game.Officials: Chris Hirano,  Chris Chapin,  Kim Case
